Aku hanya bercanda.

738
00:54:53,922 --> 00:54:56,383
Jangan memintaku menikahimu lagi,
kau mengerti?

739
00:55:02,180 --> 00:55:03,556
<i>Aku tak bisa bernapas.</i>

740
00:55:04,516 --> 00:55:05,892
<i>Aku tenggelam.</i>

741
00:55:06,518 --> 00:55:09,271
<i>Apa hubungannya dengan ibuku?</i>

742
